8ba81b26","tid":340403,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:02:05.000Z","msg":"賽前咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebb35a3712e713fd4abf5e7a22a4668b54d8b6d","tid":340403,"uid":80832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:15:35.000Z","msg":"打假拳"},{"pid":"b9d9d682b137ed1203826e9c1673d569a43b98bd","tid":340403,"uid":5006,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"好撚on9<br />\n成個感覺都好似輸左都唔撚認輸<br />\n仲要話咩永遠強者<br />\n<br />\n打前聲大大 輸左又搵野黎講<br />\n中國人真係好撚垃閪圾<br />\n又唔輸得 又要自傲但又要輸得柒<br />\n<br />\n如果你一早謙d 輸左又認自己打得唔好<br />\n一定會更受人尊敬<br />\n<br />\n不過咩國家就出咩選手<br />\n我覺得係共匪搞到成個國家咁撚樣<br />\n樣樣野又要面 大而無當 傻傻閪閪呃飯食<br />\n領導層都on撚99成日講埋晒d口號<br />\n搞到成個國家d人都係咁撚柒款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中共快撚d滅亡就最好 <br />\n廢事遺禍人間"},{"pid":"b4b34e70e8760293089e46d398ca4140d613e4cc","tid":340403,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462b6f792b7afa26f97596479397b39f00178f4e","tid":340403,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9285ccfeb080ec7724ea360a8c4cc05fff5d87d","tid":340403,"uid":2892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"佢個仔好撚得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6ce878afdb0f776fa3ce5c8649d74346020b42","tid":340403,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:00:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢咁回應冇問題"},{"pid":"6f40a355e1a4989279127f489922885fcacc90ed","tid":340403,"uid":44525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T00:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁佢都打左好多年<br />\n我又唔覺佢輸有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係垃圾 咁都好笑<br />\n我打開拳  好耐之前就有睇過佢打拳</blockquote><br />\n吓<br />\n我睇佢奧運比賽果d打法<br />\n拎咗一點之後成場係咁走<br />\n對手比佢搞到燥晒<br />\n佢就再搵空檔又拎分<br />\n完全唔明佢點係職業賽做到世界冠軍<br />\n利申 冇睇過佢職業賽"}]}